---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import prismCover from "../images/prismCover.webp"
import trekCover from "../images/trekCover.webp"
import guidanceCover from "../images/guidanceCover.webp"
const { showSubtitle } = Astro.props;
---
<div class="flex flex-wrap container mx-auto justify-center my-[64px] items-start px-[20px]">
  {(showSubtitle) && 
    <div class="flex w-full justify-center">
      <h2 class="text-5xl mb-[48px]">Books</h2>
    </div>
  }
  <div class="flex items-stretch justify-center">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap w-[30%] rounded-[20px] bg-[#d3e3fd] p-[20px] mr-[3%]">
      <div class="flex w-full mb-[24px]">
        <Image src={prismCover} alt="Prism" class="rounded-[20px] max-h-[400px] w-auto" />
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap w-full">
        <p class="flex w-full text-lg">
          Prism is the first book in a series about various planets settled from Earth. Each presents a unique problem based on the planet's biosphere that is impacting the ability of humanity to continue living there. Investigators are sent to try to help.
        </p>
        <div class="flex w-full justify-center items-start">
          <a href="/books/prism" class="text-white hover:text-black bg-blue-700 hover:bg-green-300 rounded-[24px] px-[16px] py-[8px] mt-[24px]">Read more</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="flex flex-wrap w-[30%] rounded-[20px] bg-[#d3e3fd] p-[20px] mr-[3%]">
      <div class="flex w-full mb-[24px]">
        <Image src={trekCover} alt="Trek" class="rounded-[20px] max-h-[400px] w-auto" />
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap w-full">
        <p class="flex w-full text-lg">
          Trek is the second book in a series about various planets settled from Earth. Each presents a problem based on the planet's unique biosphere that is impacting humanityâ€™s life on the planet.
        </p>
        <div class="flex w-full justify-center items-start">
          <a href="/books/trek" class="text-white hover:text-black bg-blue-700 hover:bg-green-300 rounded-[24px] px-[16px] py-[8px] mt-[24px]">Read more</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="flex flex-wrap w-[30%] rounded-[20px] bg-[#d3e3fd] p-[20px]">
      <div class="flex w-full mb-[24px]">
        <Image src={guidanceCover} alt="The Guidance" class="rounded-[20px] max-h-[400px] w-auto" />
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap w-full">
        <p class="flex w-full text-lg">
          The Guidance is a science fiction book with a message, at least a message the author wants to deliver. Imagine the forces of the universe. How do you envision these forces? What do you think are their abilities?
        </p>
        <div class="flex w-full justify-center items-start">
          <a href="/books/the-guidance" class="text-white hover:text-black bg-blue-700 hover:bg-green-300 rounded-[24px] px-[16px] py-[8px] mt-[24px]">Read more</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
</div>